    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You send negative energy coursing through a creature that you can see within range, causing it searing pain. The target must make a &amp;Reference[con]{Constitution} saving throw. It takes 7d8 + 30 &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p>A &amp;Reference[humanoid]{humanoid} killed by this spell rises at the start of your next turn as a zombie that is permanently under your command, following your &amp;Reference[vocal]{verbal} orders to the best of its ability.</p>\n</div>",
